OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FGlass bottles excluded from
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fdeposit return plans       
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The government's latest plans for a    
OL,6, deposit return scheme for drinks       
OL,7, containers have been criticised for    
OL,8, excluding glass bottles.               
OL,10,FThe scheme due to be introduced in 2025
OL,11,Fin England, Wales and Northern Ireland 
OL,12,Fwill cover plastic bottles and cans.   
OL,14,FAccording to the proposals supermarkets
OL,15,Fwill host "reverse vending machines"   
OL,16,Fwhere bottles are returned for money.  
OL,18,FThe government says the UK uses more   
OL,19,Fthan 20 billion bottles and cans each  
OL,20,Fyear, many of which end up in landfill.
